basics.name: Hannah M. Paine
basics.label: UX/UI Designer
basics.summary: Hannah Paine is a student at Eastern Washington University working towards her degree in Visual Communication Design with a User Experience Design Certificate. She aspires to be someone who inspires others to be passionate about what they do, create and who they are. Hannah wants to be a part of something that betters the world while propelling it forward in thinking and technology. Her soul is filled with passion and fire that fuel everything she does.
